Psalm 118:15/XX/PR

/SCC/XXOMMENTARY/XX. The seven /IThakafot/XX invoke the many sets of seven circles in
Jewish tradition--the seven circles of bride and groom, of Jerichoòs falling
walls, of the /ITbimah/XX on Sukkot, and of the weekòs cycles of light and dark
as the earth revolves on its axis. Seven are the days from Sukkot to Shemini
Atzeret and seven times seven days from Pesah/± to Shavuot.    /SC/XXE.M./XX/PR

